        <xref ref="infer-workflow-ht-diagram"/>.
      </p>

      <figure xml:id="infer-workflow-ht-diagram">
        <caption><c>infer</c> package workflow for hypothesis testing.</caption>
        <image source="images/flowcharts/infer/ht_diagram_trimmed.png" width="100%">
          <description>A flowchart showing the infer package workflow for hypothesis testing: specify, hypothesize, generate, calculate, and visualize steps.</description>
        </image>
      </figure>

      <p>
